Changed from `Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *` to an explicit allowlist: `bob.jc1.tech`, `bob20250810.web.app`, `bob20250810.firebaseapp.com`, localhost. Also added `X-Firebase-AppCheck` to allowed headers.

### 4. `maxInstances` caps on expensive AI functions
`priorityNow`/`replanDay` → 3 instances, `autoEnrichTasks`/`taskStoryConversion`/`plannerLLM` → 5 instances. This prevents runaway scale bills from a burst.

